{
  "title": "ISic001553. I.Sicily inscription 001553",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰθιοκασία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰθιοκασία\"><span data-text=\"Ἰθιοκασία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰθιοκασία\">Ἰθι<span class=\"underline\">ο</span>κασία</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἥρυσα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἥρυς\">ἥρυ̣σα</span>  <span data-text=\"ἀγαθά\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἀγαθός\">ἀγαθά</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Ἰθιοκασία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰθιοκασία\">Ἰθιοκασία</span>  <span data-text=\"ἥρυσα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἥρυς\">ἥρυσα</span>  <span data-text=\"ἀγαθά\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἀγαθός\">ἀγαθά</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰθιοκασία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰθιοκασία\"><span data-text=\"Ἰθιοκασία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰθιοκασία\">ΙΘΙ<span class=\"underline\">Ο</span>ΚΑΣΙΑ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἥρυσα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἥρυς\">ΗΡ.ΣΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἀγαθά\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἀγαθός\">ΑΓΑΘΑ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Ἰθιοκασία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰθιοκασία\">ΙΘΙΟΚΑΣΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἥρυσα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἥρυς\">ΗΡΥΣΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἀγαθά\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἀγαθός\">ΑΓΑΘΑ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001553_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001553_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001553.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001553-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text checked against photograph in Vento</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"line 1\">line.1: <span>Gabrici: ΙΘΙΟΚΑΣΙΑ ΗΡΥΣΑ ΑΓΑΘΑ; Manni Piraino: Ἰθι[. .]ασία ἥρ[υ]σα ἀγαθά</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Photograph in Vento is excellent and it is possible to see traces of almost the entire text, as originally read by Gabrici. </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 50.0993 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 42.1845 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 04.0043 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Kretschmer 1927 307 no.4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002533\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002533</a>  </li><li> Gabrici 1929 55-56 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001976\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001976</a>  </li><li> Bisi 1970 101 no.5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002148\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002148</a>  </li><li> Manni Piraino 1973 23 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531</a>  </li><li> Vento 2000 88-91 tav.53-55 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001525\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001525</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Simple letters with slight serfis to the strokes, particularly to the top of the alpha. Alpha is broad with straight bar. The initial theta appears circular with a central point; the final theta has a detached horizontal bar and is slightly ovoid.</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
